title: Caithness Glass Millefiori Garden Paperweight
description:
Millefiori means 'a thousand flowers' in Italian, a fitting description for this little gathering of glass flowers, each exquisitely vying for attention in this crystal garden. Each Caithness paperweight is a unique work of art, designed by a member of their dedicated design team and hand-crafted to the highest standards by skilled makers in Scotland.

Size:  3. 1 in. x 3.1 in.
